{
  "id": "63ce7ac7ae26e5001ec168f9",
  "title": "十分条件と必要条件",
  "created": 1674476232,
  "updated": 1700555340,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63ce7ac7ae26e5001ec168f9",
      "text": "十分条件と必要条件",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476232,
      "updated": 1674476232
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7ac95e90c000001fda1e",
      "text": "from [論理と集合から始める数学の基礎 読書会]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476232,
      "updated": 1674476232
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7acd5e90c000001fda30",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476236,
      "updated": 1674476236
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7ac95e90c000001fda1f",
      "text": "十分条件と必要条件",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476232,
      "updated": 1674476232
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7ac95e90c000001fda20",
      "text": " 変数[$ x]の変域を[$ U]として、[$ P(x),Q(x)]を自由変数[$ x]の述語であるとする",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476232,
      "updated": 1674476232
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7ac95e90c000001fda21",
      "text": " [$ P(x)]の[真理集合]が[$ Q(x)]の真理集合の[部分集合]である場合",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476232,
      "updated": 1674476232
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7ac95e90c000001fda22",
      "text": "  は、このようになる[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476232,
      "updated": 1674476232
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7ac95e90c000001fda23",
      "text": "   [$ \\{x|P(x)\\}\\subset\\{x|Q(x)\\}]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476232,
      "updated": 1674476232
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7ac95e90c000001fda24",
      "text": " このとき、[$ P(x)]は[$ Q(x)]の[十分条件] ([sufficient condition]) 、[$ Q(x)]は[$ P(x)]の[必要条件] ([necessary condition]) である、という",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476232,
      "updated": 1674476232
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7ac95e90c000001fda25",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476232,
      "updated": 1674476253
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7ad45e90c000001fda31",
      "text": "例[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476243,
      "updated": 1674476245
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7ac95e90c000001fda26",
      "text": " 変数[$ x]の変域を[$ \\N]として、[$ P(x),Q(x)]を自由変数[$ x]の述語であるとする",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476232,
      "updated": 1674476245
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7ac95e90c000001fda27",
      "text": " [$ P(x)]が「[$ x+1=2]」、[$ Q(x)]が「[$ x^2-3x+2=0]」としよう",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476232,
      "updated": 1674476245
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7ac95e90c000001fda28",
      "text": " このとき[$ P(x),Q(x)]の真理集合は",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476232,
      "updated": 1674476245
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7ac95e90c000001fda29",
      "text": "  [$ \\{x|P(x)\\}=\\{1\\}]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476232,
      "updated": 1674476245
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7ac95e90c000001fda2a",
      "text": "  [$ \\{x|Q(x)\\}=\\{1,2\\}]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476232,
      "updated": 1674476245
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7ac95e90c000001fda2b",
      "text": " したがって[$ P(x)]の[真理集合]は[$ Q(x)]の真理集合の[部分集合]である",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476232,
      "updated": 1674476245
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7ac95e90c000001fda2c",
      "text": "  [$ \\{x|P(x)\\}\\subset\\{x|Q(x)\\}]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476232,
      "updated": 1674476245
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7ada5e90c000001fda32",
      "text": " このとき、[$ P(x)]は[$ Q(x)]の[十分条件]、[$ Q(x)]は[$ P(x)]の[必要条件] である",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476249,
      "updated": 1674476311
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7af95e90c000001fda33",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476280,
      "updated": 1674476280
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7ac95e90c000001fda2d",
      "text": "[$ P(x)]が[$ Q(x)]の十分条件であり、かつ必要条件でもあるときは[$ P(x)]は[$ Q(x)]の[必要十分条件]([necessary and sufficient condition])という",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476232,
      "updated": 1674476249
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7ac95e90c000001fda2e",
      "text": " これは[$ P(x) \\iff Q(x)]と同じ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476232,
      "updated": 1674476249
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7ac95e90c000001fda2f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476232,
      "updated": 1674476232
    },
    {
      "id": "655b269371fa0800001952a0",
      "text": "table:if-then",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1700472468,
      "updated": 1700472480
    },
    {
      "id": "655b26a071fa0800001952a2",
      "text": " A\tB\tA -> B",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1700472480,
      "updated": 1700472487
    },
    {
      "id": "655b26a771fa0800001952a3",
      "text": " 0\t0\t1",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1700472488,
      "updated": 1700472492
    },
    {
      "id": "655b26ac71fa0800001952a4",
      "text": " 0\t1\t1",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1700472492,
      "updated": 1700472495
    },
    {
      "id": "655b26af71fa0800001952a5",
      "text": " 1\t0\t0",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1700472496,
      "updated": 1700472500
    },
    {
      "id": "655b26b471fa0800001952a6",
      "text": " 1\t1\t1",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1700472501,
      "updated": 1700472502
    },
    {
      "id": "655b269371fa0800001952a1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1700472468,
      "updated": 1700472504
    },
    {
      "id": "655b26b771fa0800001952a7",
      "text": " [$ A \\to B]を満たすには、[$ B]が真であることが必要なので、[$ B]が必要条件 という覚え方をしている[biwa.icon]",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1700472503,
      "updated": 1700554463
    },
    {
      "id": "655b28db71fa0800001952b1",
      "text": "  [$ A]が真の時、[$ B]は真である必要がある。",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1700473053,
      "updated": 1700473085
    },
    {
      "id": "655b28e471fa0800001952b2",
      "text": "  [$ B]が真の時、[$ A]はなんでも良い。",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1700473061,
      "updated": 1700473082
    },
    {
      "id": "655b290071fa0800001952b3",
      "text": "  微妙な覚え方だ",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1700473089,
      "updated": 1700473089
    },
    {
      "id": "655b29d471fa0800002eacb7",
      "text": "  [$ A]を仮定したときに、[$ B]が真である必要がある という言い方もできる",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1700473301,
      "updated": 1700473317
    },
    {
      "id": "655b29ea71fa0800002eacba",
      "text": "　　覚え方としては本人が覚えられればなんでもいいけどロジックは微妙だな[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1700473323,
      "updated": 1700497139
    },
    {
      "id": "655b86f3aff09e00007600e7",
      "text": "　　 「[$ A \\to B]を満たすには、[$ B]が真であれば十分」とも言えるので。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1700497140,
      "updated": 1700497201
    },
    {
      "id": "655b8744aff09e00007600e8",
      "text": "　　 あ、そもそも「[$ A \\to B]を満たすには、[$ B]が真であることが必要」はFalseだね",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1700497221,
      "updated": 1700497254
    },
    {
      "id": "655b8765aff09e00007600e9",
      "text": "　　 　AがFalseのときも満たすから。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1700497254,
      "updated": 1700497275
    },
    {
      "id": "655c66b871fa080000c16f93",
      "text": "　　　[\" [$ A \\to B]を満たすには、[$ B]が真であることが必要なので、[$ B]が必要条件] は、脳内からパッと出てくる言葉で、論理的に正確な説明は、下の二行で説明している[biwa.icon]",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1700554425,
      "updated": 1700554514
    },
    {
      "id": "655b86e2aff09e00007600e6",
      "text": "\t\t\tあー、なるほど、理解[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1700497123,
      "updated": 1700555184
    },
    {
      "id": "655c69abaff09e000008826c",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t[[わかる〜！！.icon]]「[$ A \\to B]を満たすには、[$ B]が真の必要っぽさあるよね〜〜」[[逆わかる〜！！.icon]]「わかる〜」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1700555180,
      "updated": 1700555316
    },
    {
      "id": "655c69cdaff09e000008826d",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tということね、それはわかる〜",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1700555213,
      "updated": 1700555340
    },
    {
      "id": "655c6a3aaff09e000008826e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1700555323,
      "updated": 1700555323
    }
  ]
}